data.description: Welcome to the Club Cottage section of Callawassie Island. Conveniently located close to the core amenities of the community's Main Club House, Fitness Facility, Pickle Ball Courts, Tennis, Swimming Pool and Practice Range. This 3 bedroom/3 bath home features tranquil long views of marsh, golf and a rear lagoon setting. The Club Cottages offer short term rental opportunities for the investor as well as a primary resident.
